    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Repairing holes or tears in woven fabric by adding supplemental threads to duplicate as nearly as possible the weave and tension of the original fabric.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
